Class Table

  • java.lang.Object
    • Table
  • public class Table
extends java.lang.Object
    Table is the class for aggregating Student into one table group. The size of the table is set at the instantiation of a Table object, and is unchangeable thereafter. The class also provides the following fields:
    • The x coordinate of the table
    • The y coordinate of the table
    • The radius of the table
    Version:
    1.0, 02/14/20
    Author:
    Charles Wong, Cindy Wang
